{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2013/01/shennongjia-ski-tour/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/film/","name":"独立电影与短片"}],"tags":[{"name":"游船","path":"/tag/cruise/"},{"name":"滑雪","path":"/tag/ski/"},{"name":"神农架","path":"/tag/shennongjia/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/a3.jpg"},"path":"/2013/01/shennongjia-ski-tour/","date":"2013-01-08T13:29:29.000Z","excerpt":"2013年第一天，和朋友们去神农架滑雪。滑雪场位于距离木鱼镇35公里的天燕阁景区，滑雪场不是很大，有初级、中级 … ","title":"快餐式神农架滑雪之旅","content":"<p>2013年第一天，和朋友们去神农架滑雪。滑雪场位于距离木鱼镇35公里的天燕阁景区，滑雪场不是很大，有初级、中级两条滑雪道，不过对于我们来体验下滑雪的足够了。</p>\n<p>中途去的那个昭君村景区很差劲，坐游船过西陵峡很过瘾！</p>\n<p><object width=\"500\" height=\"375\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNDk4NzA1OTk2/v.swf\" /><embed width=\"500\" height=\"375\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNDk4NzA1OTk2/v.swf\" /></object></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MtEued1WEj0\" target=\"_blank\">在youtube上观看</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2013/01/shennongjia-ski-tour/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}